sentences.english: The types and homogenizing principles of blending silos were described.
sentences.chinese: 介紹了粉體混料倉的型式及摻混原理。

sentences.english: Once the flow channel has emptied, all flow from the silo stops.
sentences.chinese: 一旦流動通道被排空，料倉中的所有流動就停止了。

sentences.english: Setting condition of reverse wind system in polyethylene materials storehouse have been analyzed.
sentences.chinese: 分析了目前聚乙烯料倉反吹風系統的設置情況。
